post.summary:
Detects objects in an image using few-shot AI detection (GECO2).
The user provides an image URL and 1-3 exemplar bounding boxes;
the AI locates all similar objects and returns the count + annotated image.

AIDetectRequest.description:
Request to detect objects in an image using AI (GECO2 few-shot detection).
The user provides 1-3 exemplar bounding boxes as reference samples; 
the AI then locates all similar objects in the image.
